Start
/ Test: sign with custom contracts, verify with matching contracts
- archive identity 'testSigner', force, on error ignore
- create identity testSigner
- set %data% = { "payload": 42 }
- sign %data% with contracts ['C0', 'C1']
- verify %data% with contracts ['C0', 'C1'], write to %verifyResult%
- assert %verifyResult.Success% is true, "matching custom contracts should verify"
